  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What is Space Struck Run?</h2>Space Struck Run is a small game where you take control of Dectron The Cyborg, where you have to do your best to survive in outer space while the difficulty keeps rising. <br>Avoid falling to the emptiness of space thanks to dectron’s gravity boots, survive by jumping over the enemy ships!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/994650/extras/71e21e39db7d9762fe6e156eed3e7dba.poster.avif?t=1587274462\" width=650 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/994650/extras/71e21e39db7d9762fe6e156eed3e7dba.webm?t=1587274462\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/994650/extras/71e21e39db7d9762fe6e156eed3e7dba.mp4?t=1587274462\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The difficulty will increase as the player survival score increases<br></li><li>Deal with multiple obstacles such as explosive drones over the spaceships and asteroids.<br></li><li>Use your energy shield to avoid getting killed by energy blasts and explosive drones.<br></li><li>Steam leaderboards and achievements will come soon after release.</li></ul>",
